<item>
            <title>[LU-7377] ldiskfs format requires ZFS modules</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7377</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Attempting to format MDT as ldiskfs with --backfstype=ldiskfs option. The format fails if ZFS modules are not loaded. Error is:&lt;br/&gt;
Failed to initialize ZFS library&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;modprobe zfs fixes this issue, but should not be required for ldiskfs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
